--- !u!114 &1292508660
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1292508659}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 971bd4697be894a48af86332a1394287, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Scene8SequenceController
  introLines:
  - name: Narrative
    text: '[The elevator doors open. A cold blue light floods the room. Rows of server
      racks stretch endlessly, connected by glowing cables.]'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: Yves
    text: "\u2026 This feels like a maze."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: a9b57e6b58812f6408ab5ca487fc6896, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Narrative
    text: '[Spooky.]'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: Yves
    text: "One wrong move and I\u2019m fried\u2026 great."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3ff805cf415904548a2b5b7b3f2634cb, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Tala
    text: Oooh~ Lechon for dinner!
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 589e5d9bb2540e9449ff9821b90f20be, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Yves
    text: Really, Tala?
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 161d6552c26384f4b8837755fa01ef96, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Tala
    text: HEHE
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 5db67cf600e5b48449e5cb01e8b81c00, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  ambushLines:
  - name: Narrative
    text: '[Enemies appear: File Flingers throwing sharp folder-like projectiles.]'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: Narrative
    text: "[Yves doesn\u2019t notice the incoming attack towards him.]"
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: Tala
    text: YVES! BEHIND YOU!
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 262a976ce482d7f45b6adb88b33ef6b3, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Narrative
    text: '[Yves is startled by Tala out of nowhere then he dodges the attack to
      counter attack.]'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: Yves
    text: Woah, That was a close one. Thanks, Tala.
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 21d2f0ed201594747887c027d38e77a9, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Tala
    text: '*sighs* What are you without me?'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: bffd5292b25f8a94abf7ea7c85385f8a, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Yves
    text: Yeah yeah.
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 289033378404d424bae59f81f8e8c1a3, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  questioningLines:
  - name: Narrative
    text: '[Yves looks around the floor and suddenly has the courage to question
      her since the beginning at the clinic.]'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: Yves
    text: "\u2026"
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: Tala
    text: Uh.. Are you gonna say something?
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 75f03afd36ca85d4788d980cf5ecb408, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Narrative
    text: "[Yves looks at Tala and looks like he\u2019s hesitating to say something.]"
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: Yves
    text: "Uhhh\u2026 I have been holding this since we met in the clinic."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 871fc475cd6e74c4d877e5811999d340, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Tala
    text: Stop edging me and say it already!
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 9e53f57495c40db48b9a2e0485cdc96a, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Narrative
    text: '[Yves got courage and delight but continued speaking.]'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: Yves
    text: Okay first question, how did you find me and how did I end up at the clinic
      with Nurse Loren?
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: e7a31482ef827e54baaecd50d463aac7, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Tala
    text: "You\u2019ll know the other details later but I was the one who rescued
      you from [REDACTED] and brought you somewhere Nurse Loren can see you."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 58a803049254c944889eccb7b7a33145, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Narrative
    text: '[Yves was surprised and delighted because of why he was here and going
      forward to find some answers about this world.]'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: Yves
    text: "I don\u2019t understand.."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 4d33a7f7cef606347948c3f790733e3c, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Tala
    text: You will, soon.
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3a5b2132a9b6a7b469eac287303922af, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Yves
    text: "It just doesn\u2019t make sense.."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 196221dd1db432842b8f9084c3a6c56f, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Tala
    text: Quit your babbling, do you have any other questions?
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: c73b417229823d2469050312c5b20850, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Narrative
    text: "[Yves starts working while tala floats beside him while yves\u2019s walking
      to start finding the next elevator.]"
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: Yves
    text: Give me a second.
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 6afdefb1ed39e874d82155e1c73e66a2, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Narrative
    text: '[Yves thinks about many possible questions but then goes to the one he
      thinks the most of all.]'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: Yves
    text: "I\u2019m pretty sure that you were once a person.. How did you end up
      like.. That? A glowy bubble."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: e0e3368050e7876468680e568ec2c292, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Narrative
    text: '[Tala was speechless and thought about the situation of the place.]'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: Tala
    text: "It all started at the Expo\u2026"
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: b93b3c59667a0954f98e3b256af02b8b, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  flashbackLab1:
  - name: Narrative
    text: '[Timeframe from 10 years of STI when [REDACTED] was a young bright student
      of STI.]'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: Tala
    text: '[REDACTED] was a hardworking student with big ideas and a prodigious amount
      of ICT.'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3cc16f0f06588b548be6296a252ebb13, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Damon
    text: "Tala! Where are the writers and artists? They need to finish the script
      to continue the game we\u2019re developing."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: ad710c9e067d2ba44ac240d2e006a109, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Tala
    text: "Our members are working on it, don't be obsessive on the game, Damon.
      You need some rest, isn\u2019t that why I\u2019m your partner? I\u2019m looking
      after you, so you don\u2019t overwork too much."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 9c632c7b9de9dbf4d9a535cc8a6ab6d9, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Tala
    text: "That\u2019s where [REDACTED] was being so obsessive to finish the game
      because of how much time he wasted on it\u2026 He needs some rest or his mind
      gets corrupted and collapses once the Expo starts. But one day at the laboratory\u2026"
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 0729b33f2320c70418f3e6e052e60eae, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Tala
    text: "You really won\u2019t listen, all these food I gave you are untouched!
      Damon, I am seriously getting annoyed. Eat this and rest before something happens
      to you!"
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 4622165950d3af34bae97c92d8ca008f, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Narrative
    text: '[Damon ignores Tala and continues working on the game. A couple of minutes
      later, Damon replies to Tala.]'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: Damon
    text: "Tala, I\u2019m almost done just give me about an hour-"
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 9f328f670a0cf414fb2a5d1fd6f7aee9, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Narrative
    text: '[Tala cuts Damon off his speaking to reply on it quickly.]'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: Tala
    text: "AN HOUR!? DAMON, YOU HAVEN\u2019T EATEN ANYTHING THE WHOLE DAY! STOP WORKING
      ON THE GAME AND EAT!"
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 042dc6ed2067f6a4c834b62b69b46b1f, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Tala
    text: "That\u2019s when the malware happens in the game\u2026 Damon is so obsessed
      with developing the game he doesn\u2019t realize that the virus is already
      growing inside the game then\u2026 While we both argued with each other."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 910d8ee2c8388784e9c4ccb8df62622e, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Narrative
    text: '[Tala excitedly came over to Damon to show the progress of the game.]'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: Tala
    text: "Damon, have you seen the script? It matches our imaginations so we- Huh..?
      What\u2019s this?"
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 8f9637956f12fc74bb36f018c1f7bc8c, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  flashbackLab2:
  - name: Narrative
    text: '[Damon looks at his computer and rushes to remove the virus but the internet
      was too slow. The computer starts glitching slightly red.]'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: Damon
    text: Wait.. WAIT! AGHH NO. STUPID WIFI, I WAS ALMOST THERE TO REMOVE THE VIRUS!
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: c00fb701c54b76d4bb5ff4cbb7f894b2, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Narrative
    text: '[Damon started to type to counter the malware but in zero progress malware
      started to possess Damon.]'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: Tala
    text: "Hey.. H-HEY DAMON?!? WHAT\u2019S HAPPENING TO YO-"
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: ee82e2c5423ca4941ac77216ede7e869, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  flashbackRuined1:
  - name: Narrative
    text: '[They pass out, then they are suddenly on an alternate timeline where
      the STI College Caloocan is ruined because of the malware destroying the world.
      STI College Caloocan is the only fortress with the power to fix everything
      left]'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: '[REDACTED]'
    text: AAGGHHH! THIS IS YOUR FAULT!
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 7fb00992a023dfd418cc0a72ac2e5119, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Narrative
    text: "[Damon then strangles Tala\u2019s neck causing her to die of suffocation.]"
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  flashbackRuined2:
  - name: Tala
    text: "D-Damon.. P-please.. I-I can\u2019t.. B-breathe.. Damo-"
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 390e87f6f1cfb384b86052546eb72007, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Damon
    text: "Tala..? Wait, wait no. I-I can still fix this.. Tala, wake up please..
      I can\u2019t do this without you.. I\u2019m sorry."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 6d99931f8a9ef9a4c8510eb91be95fcb, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Narrative
    text: '[After what corrupted Damon did to Tala, his emotions got to him and transformed
      into the most powerful corrupted virus that has ever existed.]'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: '[REDACTED]'
    text: YOU DESERVE THAT FOR ALWAYS NAGGING ME.
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 2d472999359944e45a0167d8fd182efe, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Damon
    text: "I should\u2019ve listened to you.."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 9799fe91e93cb114abf42e58e2e83b2a, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Narrative
    text: '[Glitching the looks of Damon and REDACTED, the two speaks in one body
      but glitching into two.]'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  endingLines:
  - name: Tala
    text: "That\u2019s what happened to Damon and started this hell of a nightmare
      in STI."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 7bac61c70393b584e80ddcd04363519f, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Narrative
    text: '[The timeframe stops and back from the present time.]'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: Narrative
    text: '[Yves passes the last trap from the maze to the next elevator.]'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
  - name: Yves
    text: "Don\u2019t worry, tala. I.. I have a feeling that we can still bring back
      Damon."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 697cdaeb3077ea34396eaf2b1f80e828, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Tala
    text: "That\u2019s.. Impossible, Yves. The only thing that you can do is defeat
      [REDACTED] but bring Damon back? He\u2019s gone."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: bbd2fe7ad1dc7a84e8529753ab6d3bbf, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Tala
    text: "I don\u2019t think I've told you this, but in order to defeat him, you
      have to get the final source code from the Library. Then, you\u2019ll inject
      the quantum computer on the Penthouse in order to stop things\u2026 And hopefully\u2013
      go back to our original timeline."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: a6b41fd71bdcfd34c80ef111407c6bd7, type: 3}
    volume: 1
  - name: Narrative
    text: '[Screen fades.]'
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    volume: 1
